the roots of things

00:33:03.290 --> 00:33:05.370
seems like a good strategy.

00:33:05.370 --> 00:33:08.420
We have an office in
Kampala, with Googlers there.

00:33:08.420 --> 00:33:10.590
We have many offices,
actually, across Africa

00:33:10.590 --> 00:33:11.620
