business flourishes.

00:34:18.170 --> 00:34:20.866
And I think there's a
way that an organization

00:34:20.866 --> 00:34:23.449
like the International Gay and
Lesbian Human Rights Commission

00:34:23.449 --> 00:34:24.429
can make that.

00:34:24.429 --> 00:34:27.929
