00:34:33.380 --> 00:34:36.090
Just to kind of flag,
there are huge issues

00:34:36.090 --> 00:34:40.580
around the safety and security
of LGBT people online going far

00:34:40.580 --> 00:34:41.730
beyond these countries.

00:34:41.730 --> 00:34:43.960
There are instances
of internet entrapment

00:34:43.960 --> 00:34:46.310
