communities around the world.

00:34:55.670 --> 00:34:57.410
I actually think it's
one of the reasons

00:34:57.410 --> 00:35:00.070
that we've seen so much
progress in the past five years

00:35:00.070 --> 00:35:01.870
because people can
find each other.

00:35:01.870 --> 00:35:03.475
And when you can
find each other,

00:35:03.475 --> 00:35:05.600
you can start doing this
movement-based work that's

00:35:05.600 --> 00:35:07.090
so important.

00:35:07.090 --> 00:35:08.870
But then the question
is, how do you

00:35:08.870 --> 00:35:12.810
help make sure people are
consuming internet services

00:35:12.810 --> 00:35:15.520
safely so that they
can find each other?

00:35:15.520 --> 00:35:17.130
And we know of many
governments that

00:35:17.130 --> 00:35:21.940
have set up entrapment
strategies that have resulted

00:35:21.940 --> 00:35:25.540
in a range of horrors
for LGBT people.

00:35:25.540 --> 00:35:28.345
I don't know what Google does
around safety and security,

00:35:28.345 --> 00:35:30.720
but I think that would be
really important to talk about.

