00:41:20.720 --> 00:41:21.875
or not care?

00:41:21.875 --> 00:41:23.490
Does that makes sense?

00:41:23.490 --> 00:41:25.300
JESSICA STERN: Yeah, it does.

00:41:25.300 --> 00:41:29.630
Yes, the rule of law exists,
